<title>whnfrḥ brḍw hnfrḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bnḥzn wnkẖạf rbmạ wạlsẖr yswd
 ạ̹nmạ
 ạ̉frạḥnạ bṭʿm ạlsmạ wtẖmạr ạlfrḥ htṭrḥ
 nfrḥ bạlḍạl ạlrạjʿ bdmwʿ ạltwbẗ wrạkʿ
 mrmy fy ạlḥḍn ạlwạsʿ wạlsmạ bạltạyẗ tfrḥ
 ạlqrạr- whnfrḥ brḍw hnfrḥ wnrnm lk wnsbḥ
 wmʿạk yạ ḥbybnạ hnfrḥ wnrnm lk wnsbḥ
 wbrgẖm ạlgẖymẗ ạlswạd dạ msyr ạlṣbḥ yṣbḥ
 2- lmạ ạlạ̉tʿạb twjʿnạ nṭlb wạ̹nt btsmʿnạ
 bạlrwḥ tyjy tjmʿnạ wqṣdk hytm wynjḥ
 bṣlạẗ wmʿạhạ ạ̉ṣwạmnạ wrjạʾ ḥy mṣyrnạ</lyrics>
